---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Guides — MinimalDev"
  description="Learn how to use tools effectively with practical guides and examples."
  canonicalPath="/guides/"
>
  <div class="container">

    <section class="card" style="padding:18px;">
      <h1 class="page-title">Guides & Practical Tips</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Learn how to use tools correctly, understand results, and choose the right approach for your task.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="card" style="padding:18px;">
        <div class="prose">

          <h2>How to Use These Guides</h2>

          <p>
            These guides are designed to help you understand not only how to use each tool, but also why certain approaches work better than others.
          </p>
          <p>
            You can read a guide first, then use the related tool to apply what you learned in practice.
          </p>

          <p>
            Each guide focuses on practical topics such as image formats, compression, calculations, and optimization.
          </p>

          <h3>What You Will Learn</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>How different formats affect quality and file size</li>
            <li>When to prioritize performance vs visual quality</li>
            <li>How to avoid common mistakes</li>
            <li>How to choose the right tool</li>
          </ul>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="grid">

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Image Guide</span>
          <h2>Image Format Comparison</h2>
          <p>PNG vs JPG vs WebP explained with real use cases.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/image-format-comparison/">Read</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Image Guide</span>
          <h2>Reduce Image Size</h2>
          <p>Understand compression and quality trade-offs.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/reduce-image-size/">Read</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Image Guide</span>
          <h2>Why Use WebP</h2>
          <p>Learn why modern websites prefer WebP.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/why-use-webp/">Read</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Image Guide</span>
          <h2>JPG vs PNG</h2>
          <p>Choose the right format based on use case.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/jpg-vs-png/">Read</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Image Guide</span>
          <h2>Image Resize Guide</h2>
          <p>Resize images properly without distortion.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/image-resize-guide/">Read</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Image Guide</span>
          <h2>Crop Image Guide</h2>
          <p>How to crop images for best composition.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/how-to-crop-image/">Read</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Image Guide</span>
          <h2>Free Image Tools</h2>
          <p>Find practical image tools for compression, cropping, conversion, and web workflows.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/free-image-tools/">Read</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Image Guide</span>
          <h2>Convert Images With Minimal Quality Loss</h2>
          <p>Learn how to choose formats and workflows that preserve image quality.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/convert-image-without-losing-quality/">Read</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Performance Guide</span>
          <h2>Image Optimization for Web</h2>
          <p>Improve loading speed with optimized images.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/image-optimization-for-web/">Read</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">General Guide</span>
          <h2>Online vs Offline Image Tools</h2>
          <p>Compare browser tools vs installed software.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/online-vs-offline-image-tools/">Read</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Developer Guide</span>
          <h2>JSON Formatting Basics</h2>
          <p>Learn how JSON formatting and validation works in real applications.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/json-formatting-basics/">Read</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Finance Guide</span>
          <h2>Loan and Interest Basics</h2>
          <p>Understand how loans, interest, and amortization affect total cost.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/loan-interest-basics/">Read</a>
        </section>

      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>